'''维基百科零计划'''（{{lang-en|Wikipedia Zero}}）是[[维基媒体基金会|维基媒体基金会]]一个项目，通过与移动运营商合作为用户提供在[[智能手机|智能手机]]上免除流量费用访问[[维基百科|维基百科]]的服务，特别是在[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.technobuffalo.com/2013/02/22/wikipedia-zero-sms/ |title=Wikipedia Zero Wants to Bring Wikipedia to Mobile Users Without a Data Plan |last=Russell |first=Brandon |date=2013-02-22 |work=''TechnoBuffalo'' |accessdate=2013-04-08 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130329194118/http://www.technobuffalo.com/2013/02/22/wikipedia-zero-sms/ |archive-date=2013-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Getting Wikipedia to the people who need it most |url=http://www.knightfoundation.org/blogs/knightblog/2013/2/22/getting-wikipedia-people-who-need-it-most/ |accessdate=2013-04-08 |date=2013-02-22 |last=Wadhwa |first=Kul Takanao |publisher=Knight Foundation |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130704041945/http://www.knightfoundation.org/blogs/knightblog/2013/2/22/getting-wikipedia-people-who-need-it-most/ |archivedate=2013-07-04 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。该计划在2012年提出<ref>{{Cite journal |title=SXSW: Wikipedia for Non-Smartphones Is Brilliant. Here's Why |url=http://www.popularmechanics.com/how-to/blog/sxsw-wikipedia-for-non-smartphones-is-brilliant-here-s-why-15189767 |last=Sofge |first=Erik |date=2013-03-08 |accessdate=2013-04-08 |work=[[Popular_Mechanics|Popular Mechanics]] |journal= |archive-date=2013-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130412020713/http://www.popularmechanics.com/how-to/blog/sxsw-wikipedia-for-non-smartphones-is-brilliant-here-s-why-15189767 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2013年3月该计划赢得了赢得[[西南偏南|西南偏南]]的“互动”奖<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/blogs/sxsw/2013-03-12/sxsw-interactive-awards-announced/ |title=SXSW Interactive Awards Announced |last=Riese |first=Monica |date=2013-03-12 |work=[[The_Austin_Chronicle|The Austin Chronicle]] |publisher=Austin Chronicle Corp. |accessdate=2013-04-08 |location=Austin, Texas |issn=1074-0740 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226132848/https://www.austinchronicle.com/daily/sxsw/2013-03-12/sxsw-interactive-awards-announced/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该计划的目的是减少访问自由数据库的成本。不过此计划多年来也受到了违背[[网络中立|网络中立]]原则的批评<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=Net Neutrality and the Global Digital Divide |url=https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2014/07/net-neutrality-and-global-digital-divide |date=2014-07-24 |work=Electronic Frontier Foundation |accessdate=2019-08-31 |archive-date=2015-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208095812/https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2014/07/net-neutrality-and-global-digital-divide |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web |title=Wikipedia Zero and net neutrality: Wikimedia turns its back on the open internet |url=https://www.accessnow.org/blog/2014/08/08/wikipedia-zero-and-net-neutrality-wikimedia-turns-its-back-on-the-open |date=August 8, 2014 |work=accessnow.org |accessdate=2019-08-31 |archive-date=2015-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104123623/https://www.accessnow.org/blog/2014/08/08/wikipedia-zero-and-net-neutrality-wikimedia-turns-its-back-on-the-open |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2018年2月，维基媒体基金会宣布结束此倡议，将改为采取新的合作方式<ref name=":2">{{Cite web |title=Building for the future of Wikimedia with a new approach to partnerships – Wikimedia Blog |url=https://blog.wikimedia.org/2018/02/16/partnerships-new-approach/ |accessdate=February 18, 2018 |work=[[Wikimedia_Foundation|Wikimedia Foundation]] |archive-date=2019-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905163603/https://blog.wikimedia.org/2018/02/16/partnerships-new-approach/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.engadget.com/2018/02/18/wikipedia-zero-ends/ |title=Wikipedia ends no-cost mobile access for developing countries |last=Fingas |first=Jon |date=February 18, 2018 |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |accessdate=February 19, 2018 |archive-date=2019-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204132737/https://www.engadget.com/2018/02/18/wikipedia-zero-ends/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Facebook Zero}}计划据称灵感来自维基百科零计划<ref>{{Cite web |title=Wikipedia Zero: free data if you can afford it |url=http://www.dw.de/wikipedia-zero-free-data-if-you-can-afford-it/a-17304321 |accessdate=2014-01-15 |date=2013-12-18 |last=Dillon |first=Conon |archive-date=2014-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140123090951/http://www.dw.de/wikipedia-zero-free-data-if-you-can-afford-it/a-17304321 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==发展==
维基百科零计划最早于2012年5月于[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]推出<ref>{{Cite web |title=Wikipedia Zero launches in Malaysia with Digi — Wikimedia blog |url=http://blog.wikimedia.org/2012/05/26/wikipedia-zero-launches-in-malaysia-with-digi/ |accessdate=2013-06-27 |date=2012-05-26 |publisher=Blog.wikimedia.org |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226132839/https://blog.wikimedia.org/2012/05/26/wikipedia-zero-launches-in-malaysia-with-digi/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年10月，DTAC和沙特电信公司分别在[[泰国|泰国]]与[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]推出该服务。2013年5月，Mobilink在[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]推出该服务<ref>{{Cite web |title=Mobilink brings Wikipedia Zero to Pakistan |url=http://www.nation.com.pk/pakistan-news-newspaper-daily-english-online/business/05-Jun-2013/mobilink-brings-wikipedia-zero-to-pakistan |accessdate=2013-06-27 |publisher=Nation.com.pk |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622082157/http://www.nation.com.pk/pakistan-news-newspaper-daily-english-online/business/05-Jun-2013/mobilink-brings-wikipedia-zero-to-pakistan |archivedate=2013-06-22 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2013年6月，Dialog Axiata在[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]推出该服务<ref>{{Cite web |title=Dialog brings Wikipedia Zero to Sri Lanka |url=http://www.dialog.lk/personal/mobile/features-and-vas/information-services/wikipedia-free/ |accessdate=2013-06-24 |publisher=www.dialog.lk |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715111202/http://www.dialog.lk/personal/mobile/features-and-vas/information-services/wikipedia-free/ |archivedate=2013-07-15 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。Aircel集团在[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]、马来西亚、[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]、斯里兰卡和[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]]等国推出了该服务，其中在印度尼西亚、柬埔寨、孟加拉国为首次<ref>{{Cite web |title=Aircel customers can now access Wikipedia on their mobile phones for free | NDTV Gadgets |url=http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/aircel-customers-can-now-access-wikipedia-on-their-mobile-phones-for-free-397035 |accessdate=2013-09-20 |date=2013-07-25 |publisher=Gadgets.ndtv.com |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226132840/https://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/aircel-customers-can-now-access-wikipedia-on-their-mobile-phones-for-free-397035 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年4月，印尼第二大的電信商Indosat也宣布加入這個計劃<ref>{{Cite web |title=Indosat partners with Facebook to offer free access |url=http://www.mobileworldlive.com/asia/asia-news/indosat-partners-facebook-offer-free-access/ |accessdate=2015-08-21 |author=Joseph Waring |date=2015-04-20 |publisher=Mobile World Live}}</ref>。

